Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.76,0:11:02.82,Default,Kirino,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.36,0:11:05.04,Default,Kirino,0,0,0,,{Goodbye, then.}Vậy em xin phép.
